description: Firefly Pizza Pies is a wood oven Austin pizza trailer making delicious and expertly-crafted pizzas. Firefly uses the finest imported Italian products including San Marzano tomatoes, 00 wheat flour, Extra Virgin Olive Oil, artisan meats, specialty cheeses, and more. Local organic and sustainable farms, co-ops, and suppliers provide the fresh produce and meats, and they use only the highest grade all-natural cheeses. Each product is made in-house, from scratch.Swing by and grab a delicious pizza pie today!
name: Firefly Pizza Pies
